cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with video detection, tracking, and classification systems. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as these fields are closely related to computer vision. Multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-categories are less likely but still possible as the paper mentions ground truth data and bounding box coordinates, which could be related to multimedia analysis and security applications.
